WEBVTT

00:00:01.095 --> 00:00:05.684
We live in a world
increasingly tyrannized by the screen,

00:00:05.708 --> 00:00:09.640
by our phones, by our tablets,
by our televisions and our computers.

00:00:09.664 --> 00:00:11.967
We can have any experience that we want,

00:00:11.991 --> 00:00:13.627
but feel nothing.

00:00:13.651 --> 00:00:15.574
We can have as many friends as we want,

00:00:15.598 --> 00:00:18.089
but have nobody to shake hands with.

00:00:19.667 --> 00:00:21.939
I want to take you
to a different kind of world,

00:00:21.963 --> 00:00:23.598
the world of the imagination,

00:00:23.622 --> 00:00:27.847
where, using this most powerful
tool that we have,

00:00:27.871 --> 00:00:31.065
we can transform both
our physical surroundings,